## 8. Conclusion

UTXO6‑DNS natively binds IPv6 address space with blockchain UTXO ownership via VRF, solving the three major pain points: hard‑to‑remember payment identities, difficult compliance audits, and lack of AI‑friendly on‑chain operation interfaces. The protocol is implemented in TypeScript/Python SDKs and being piloted within the CoCaDEX ecosystem. We believe this technology will become a key component of future Web3 infrastructure.

